descriptionHtml:
[color=red]This mod is ancient, there are new and better things now, and as such I\'m no longer offering support for it. If you somehow stumbled here but wanted CBBE instead then you can get [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/39301]CBBE Innies[/url] texture.[/color]

Nude Textures - Innies
by XunAmarox

Description:
Replacer for default skin. 3 different styles: shaved, strip, & bushy. The vulva is an \"innie,\" as opposed to an \"outie.\" That is, the labia minora is interior to the labia majora. 

Also includes new breasts, nipples, stomach, belly button, and a completely redone texture.  Also features an anus.

Installation:
1. Paste contents of /Data/ into /Data/
2. If you want bushy or strip, paste texture file over shaved texture file.

Included:
body texture (3 variants)
normal map
shader map
hand texture

Nothing else. Probably won\'t work for anything that doesn\'t use the default female texture.

Version History:
1.2 - [color=red]New![/color] nails added to hand texture, install after main.
1.1 - Greatly improved vulva texture
1.0 - Release
